<div class="container-fluid px-5">
  <div class="text-center mb-4">
    <h2 class="section-title">My Service Learning Experiences</h2>
    <p>View my CCA Transcript here (will put later)</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center">

    <!-- Session 1 -->
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex">
      <div class="achievement-card shadow-sm p-3 h-100 border border-primary">
        <img src="/images/youtube.jpeg" class="service-img mb-3" alt="YouTube Workshop for Seniors">
        <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">Service Learning Session 1</h5>
        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">YouTube Workshop for Seniors</h6>
        <p><strong>Role:</strong> Volunteer</p>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Guided seniors in basic YouTube navigation</li>
          <li>Demonstrated volume control and playback</li>
          <li>Explained step-by-step usage</li>
          <li>Communicated in Malay to assist Malay-speaking seniors</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Reflection:</strong><br><br>
          From this experience, I realised that explaining technical concepts in simple terms is crucial when teaching seniors.<br><br>
          I learned to be patient and empathetic, understanding that everyone learns at their own pace and to adapt my teaching approach to suit the needs of each participant.<br><br> 
          This session also improved my communication skills, and ability to engage learners with different backgrounds.<br><br>
          This experience made me more aware of the challenges seniors face when using technology and motivated me to continue volunteering and making a positive impact in my community.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Skills Gained:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Teamwork</li>
          <li>Communication</li>
          <li>Teaching</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Session 2 -->
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex">
      <div class="achievement-card shadow-sm p-3 h-100 border border-primary">
        <img src="/images/piccollage1.jpeg" class="service-img mb-3" alt="PicCollage Workshop">
        <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">Service Learning Session 2</h5>
        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">PicCollage Workshop for Seniors</h6>
        <p><strong>Role:</strong> Volunteer</p>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Guided seniors to create digital memories with PicCollage</li>
          <li>Reviewed templates, stickers, text and filters</li>
          <li>Provided one-on-one support for seniors</li>
          <li>Communicated in Malay</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Reflection:</strong><br><br>
          Guiding seniors through the PicCollage workshop showed me that digital creativity can be enjoyed by anyone, regardless of age or technical experience.<br><br>
          I learned to balance giving instructions with allowing seniors the freedom to explore independently, which not only strengthened my teaching skills but also helped build their confidence.<br><br> 
          This session also highlighted the importance of clear and culturally sensitive communication, and using Malay to connect effectively with the seniors improved my ability to engage diverse learners.<br><br>
        </p>
        <p><strong>Skills Gained:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Communication</li>
          <li>Empathy</li>
          <li>Patience</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Session 3 -->
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <div class="achievement-card">
        <img src="/images/chatgpt_workshop.jpeg" class="service-img mb-3" alt="ChatGPT Workshop">
        <h5 class="card-title">Service Learning Session 3</h5>
        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Introduction to ChatGPT for Seniors</h6>
        <p><strong>Role:</strong> Participant</p>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Introduced seniors to ChatGPT basics and practical uses</li>
          <li>Demonstrated tasks like recipes (Nasi Minyak) and learning aid examples</li>
          <li>Explained AI in simple terms and used Malay for clarity</li>
          <li>Presented in English to improve public speaking</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Reflection:</strong><br>
          Volunteering to teach seniors how to use ChatGPT was a meaningful experience that highlighted the importance of making technology like AI, accessible to all. Guiding them through basic tasks helped me appreciate how AI can support daily tasks and learning.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Skills Gained:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Communication</li>
          <li>Empathy</li>
          <li>Teaching</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Session 4 -->
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <div class="achievement-card">
        <img src="/images/capcutservicelearning.png" class="service-img mb-3" alt="Capcut Service Learning">
        <h5 class="card-title">Service Learning Session 4</h5>
        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Capcut Workshop at Greenwood Primary School</h6>
        <p><strong>Role:</strong> Student Volunteer Teacher</p>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Assigned to a group of Primary Four students to guide them during their enrichment programme using capcut</li>
          <li>Taught basic video editing skills such as trimming, velocity, transitions and effects.</li>
          <li>Explained concepts in simple, step-by-step instructions for better understanding</li>
          <li>Adapted explanations to suit students with different attention spans.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Reflection:</strong><br>
          This experience helped me develop patience and improve my ability to explain technical concepts in a clear and simple manner. Working with students of different attention spans required me to adapt my communication style.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Skills Gained:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Communication</li>
          <li>Empathy</li>
          <li>Teamwork</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Session 5 -->
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
      <div class="achievement-card">
        <img src="/images/ygos5.png" class="service-img mb-3" alt="YGOS Workshop Session 5">
        <h5 class="card-title">YGOS Workshop Session 5</h5>
        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">YGOS Treasure Hunt Activity</h6>
        <p><strong>Role:</strong> Station Master - UNO Stress Station</p>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Facilitated the UNO stress station during the YGOS treasure hunt activity</li>
          <li>Explained game rules clearly, step-by-step to youth participants before gameplay</li>
          <li>Guided participants throughout the activity to ensure smooth participation.</li>
          <li>Encouraged engagement and ensured inclusivity for all participants.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Reflection:</strong><br>
          This was another experience that helped me develop patience and adaptability when working with youths of different learning styles. I learned to adjust my explanations and approach to ensure everyone could participate comfortably.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Skills Gained:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Communication</li>
          <li>Patience & Adaptability</li>
          <li>Confidence in Leading Activities</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
